
## **1. Random Variables (RVs)**
### **Key Concepts:**  
- **Discrete RVs** (PMF, CDF)  
- **Continuous RVs** (PDF, CDF)  
- Expectation, Variance, Moments  
- Transformation of RVs  

### **Study Resources:**  
- **Video Lectures:**  
  - [Khan Academy - Random Variables](https://www.khanacademy.org/math/statistics-probability/random-variables-stats-library)  
  - [NPTEL - Probability & Statistics (IIT Kharagpur)](https://nptel.ac.in/courses/111/105/111105106/)  
- **Textbooks:**  
  - *Probability & Statistics for Engineers* – Ronald E. Walpole (Ch. 3-4)  
  - *Higher Engineering Mathematics* – B.S. Grewal (Ch. on Probability)  
- **Practice Problems:**  
  - [GATE Overflow - RV PYQs](https://gateoverflow.in/questions/tagged/random-variables)  
  - [MIT OCW Problem Sets](https://ocw.mit.edu/courses/mathematics/18-05-introduction-to-probability-and-statistics-spring-2014/assignments/)  

